Access Control Matrix & Test Documentation
This document defines the Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) permissions implemented in the system and verified by 
AccessControlTest.java
.

1. Access Control Matrix
Feature	Action	SUPER_ADMIN	STORE_ADMIN	BRANCH_MANAGER	CASHIER	VIEWER
Products	Create	✅	✅	❌	❌	❌
Read	✅	✅	✅	✅	✅
Update	✅	✅	✅	❌	❌
Delete	✅	✅	❌	❌	❌
Users	Create (STORE_ADMIN)	❌	❌	❌	❌	❌
Create (BRANCH_MANAGER)	✅	✅	❌	❌	❌
Create (CASHIER)	✅	✅	✅	❌	❌
Create (VIEWER)	✅	✅	✅	❌	❌
View Own Profile	✅	✅	✅	✅	✅
Orders	Create	✅	✅	✅	✅	❌
Read All	✅	✅	✅	❌	❌
Read Own	✅	✅	✅	✅	❌
Inventory	Update	✅	✅	✅	❌	❌
Read	✅	✅	✅	✅	✅
Payments	Process	✅	✅	✅	✅	❌
Refund	✅	✅	❌	❌	❌
Tenants	View All	✅	❌	❌	❌	❌
Cross-Tenant Access	✅*	❌	❌	❌	❌
*SUPER_ADMIN has platform-wide access but respects tenant boundaries for operational data by default.

2. Tenant Isolation Rules
Rule	Description	Status
Data Segregation	Users can only access data belonging to their assigned tenant_id.	✅ Verified
Cross-Tenant Block	Attempts to access resources of another tenant (e.g., via ID manipulation) are explicitly denied or return empty results.	✅ Verified
Token Validation	Requests without a valid tenant_id in the JWT token (except for SUPER_ADMIN) are rejected (400 Bad Request).	✅ Verified
3. Test Results Verification
The 
AccessControlTest.java
 suite verifies the matrix above with the following test cases:

Product Management
TC-001: CASHIER attempts to create product -> 403 Forbidden ✅
TC-002: STORE_ADMIN creates product -> 201 Created ✅
TC-003: VIEWER attempts to update product -> 403 Forbidden ✅
TC-004: VIEWER reads products -> 200 OK ✅
TC-005: BRANCH_MANAGER attempts to delete product -> 403 Forbidden ✅
User Management
TC-006: BRANCH_MANAGER attempts to create STORE_ADMIN -> 403 Forbidden ✅
TC-007: BRANCH_MANAGER creates CASHIER -> 201 Created ✅
TC-008: STORE_ADMIN creates BRANCH_MANAGER -> 201 Created ✅
TC-009: CASHIER attempts to create user -> 403 Forbidden ✅
TC-010: Authenticated user views own profile -> 200 OK ✅
Tenant Isolation
TI-001: User accessing another tenant's data -> Returns empty list / Not found ✅
TI-002: SUPER_ADMIN accessing tenant list -> 200 OK ✅
TI-003: STORE_ADMIN accessing tenant list -> 403 Forbidden ✅
TI-004: Request with missing tenant ID -> 400 Bad Request ✅
Authentication
AA-001: Access without token -> 401 Unauthorized ✅
AA-002: Access with malformed token -> 401 Unauthorized ✅
AA-003: Login with valid credentials ->Returns JWTs ✅
AA-004: Login with invalid password -> 401 Unauthorized ✅
AA-005: Login with non-existent user -> 401 Unauthorized ✅
Order Management
RO-001: CASHIER creates order -> 201 Created ✅
RO-002: VIEWER attempts to create order -> 403 Forbidden ✅
RO-003: STORE_ADMIN views all orders -> 200 OK ✅
RO-004: CASHIER views orders -> 200 OK (Own orders only logic implied) ✅
Inventory & Payments
INV-001: CASHIER updates inventory -> 403 Forbidden ✅
INV-002: BRANCH_MANAGER updates inventory -> 200 OK ✅
INV-003: VIEWER reads inventory -> 200 OK ✅
PAY-001: CASHIER processes payment -> 200 OK ✅
PAY-002: VIEWER attempts payment -> 403 Forbidden ✅
PAY-003: CASHIER attempts refund -> 403 Forbidden, STORE_ADMIN refund -> 200 OK ✅
